Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Grain export boycott
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b03z8q6v
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 17 Aug 1975
Fears of inflation lead to dock workers' boycott of grain shipments to USSR. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.